title: 2/1 super Cute Remodeled Heights Bungalow - walk to farmers market!
posting_body: ['Heights living at its finest!', 'Remodeled 2 Bedroom / 1 Bathroom very clean and awesome Heights bungalow ready for immediate occupancy!', 'All appliances included: full-sized washer, dryer, dishwasher, electric stove, refrigerator, microwave.', 'Central HVAC.', 'No pets, no smoking.', 'Original hardwood floors.', 'Granite counters and lots of cabinets in the kitchen.', "There's both a dining room space and a breakfast room space in this open-air concept layout.", 'One off-street driveway parking spot; a second car may park on the street.', 'Total monthly rent is $1995 which is all bills paid ($1700 base rent plus $295 for all utilities).', 'I pay for water, gas, electricity, high-speed internet, yard, and garbage pickup.', 'No application fee.', '$1500 deposit.', 'Nice-sized closets.', 'Shady back yard.', 'The garage apartment is not included.', '  Qualifications: Gross Income of 3x rent, no prior evictions/broken leases, no DWIs, no violent felonies.', 'Please call for a quick prescreening and to set up a showing today!']
